<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Mike D — Metal Fabricator</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow:wght@300;400;600&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #0a0a0a;
      --text: #f0f0f0;
      --muted: #888;
      --accent: #c0392b;
      --blue: #3a7bd5;
      --rule: #222;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 0;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* ── Banner ── */
    .banner-placeholder {
      width: 100%;
      height: 280px;
      background: #111;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .banner-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: none;
    }

    .banner-img[src]:not([src=""]) {
      display: block;
    }

    .banner-img[src]:not([src=""]) + .banner-hint {
      display: none;
    }

    .banner-hint {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* ── Main content ── */
    main {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .name {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      line-height: 1;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .name span { color: var(--accent); }

    .cert {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-top: 0.7rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.1rem;
    }

    .rule {
      width: 60px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--accent);
      margin: 1.2rem 0 1.8rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }

    .description {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #ccc;
      max-width: 540px;
    }

    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .skills {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .skills li {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #ccc;
      line-height: 1.5;
      padding-left: 1.1rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .skills li::before {
      content: '—';
      color: var(--accent);
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .skills strong {
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .contact-link {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--blue);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #1e3f70;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }

    .contact-link:hover {
      color: #6aa3f5;
      border-color: #6aa3f5;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 0 2rem 2rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #333;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- BANNER IMAGE: when ready, set src to your image path, e.g. src="banner.jpg" -->
  <div class="banner-placeholder">
    <img src="" alt="Banner" class="banner-img" />
    <span class="banner-hint">[ Banner image — insert path in src="" above ]</span>
  </div>

  <main>
    <h1 class="name">Mike D<span>.</span></h1>
    <p class="cert">AWS Certified Welding Supervisor</p>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <p class="tagline">Professional Metal Fabricator for Hire - full time or contract</p>
    <p class="description">
      Small one-off jobs, repairs, structural steel, hobby help & more!
      Steel or aluminum - if it's metal, let's talk.
    </p>
    <hr class="divider" />
    <p class="section-label">Skills &amp; Capabilities</p>
    <ul class="skills">
      <li>Structural steel in accordance with <strong>AWS D1.1</strong> and <strong>D1.3</strong></li>
      <li><strong>GMAW</strong> (MIG) — carbon steel, stainless, and aluminum</li>
      <li><strong>GTAW</strong> (TIG) — all common metals and beyond</li>
      <li><strong>FCAW</strong> (dual/self shield) — structural and heavy duty applications</li>
      <li><strong>SMAW</strong> (stick) — repair jobs, field work</li>
    </ul>
    <hr class="divider" />
    <p class="section-label">Reach out</p>
    <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:fabricator@meltdown.mozmail.com">
      fabricator@meltdown.mozmail.com
    </a>
  </main>

  <footer>© 2026 Mike D - Meltdown Fabrication</footer>

</body>
</html> 
